---
title: Coq sans Vin with bacon lardons and creamy mash
description: A twist on a classic of French cuisine, this Coq sans Vin is an impressive and flavour-filled dish—perfect to prepare for that special someone this Valentine's day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221221_R04_W07_IE_IECC13541-2_MB_Main_high-1ff1c239.jpg
